  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ControlPanel
    The view for the server.
    HomeModifier
    Modify SH3D objects properties (only the colors for the moment but can be improved)
    JSONAction
    Create a SB3 file (actually a ZIP), that is the Scratch project format, by creating a JSON and SVG to represent SH3D scene's objects
    ScratchAction
    Allow the listening of Scratch' actions and modifications on SH3D scene
    ScratchHomePlugin
    The main class of the ScratchHome plugin
    ScratchListener
    Listen actions sent by Scratch in order to modify the SH3D scene
